gw.api.archiving.upgrade

Interface IArchivedEntitySet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<IArchivedEntity>

    public interface IArchivedEntitySet
extends java.lang.Iterable<IArchivedEntity>
    Represents a set of IArchivedEntity's for the same "old" entity type.
